Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.85,0:00:41.23,main,N,0,0,0,,Mấy đứa đang làm cái gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.94,0:00:44.40,main,R,0,0,0,,Naofumi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.40,0:00:46.48,main,F,0,0,0,,Chủ nhân!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.49,0:00:48.36,main,Mel,0,0,0,,Thiệt tình!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.36,0:00:50.61,main,Mel,0,0,0,,Có cần phải ngủ lâu đến vậy không?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.32,0:00:54.03,italics,N,0,0,0,,Chuyện quái gì thế?
